org.seedstack.business.specification.dsl

Interface StringOptionPicker<T,S extends BaseSelector>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the object the specification applies to.
    S - the type of the selector.
    All Superinterfaces:
    OperatorPicker<T,S>, TerminalOperation<T>

    public interface StringOptionPicker<T,S extends BaseSelector>
extends OperatorPicker<T,S>
    An element of the SpecificationBuilder DSL to pick the options for a String-specific specification.
